---------------
Unto::Rivington
---------------

Rivington is a URL redirector.

------------
Installation
------------

First, install the Unto::Essex packages.  

Then run:

   $ perl ./Build.PL
   $ ./Build
   $ ./Build test
   $ sudo ./Build install

Then add the following lines to your httpd.conf:

  Include /usr/local/apache2/rivington/conf/httpd.conf


Create the rivington database (this may vary depending on your system):

  $ mysql --user=root -p mysql -e 'CREATE DATABASE rivington'
  $ mysql --user=root -p mysql -e "GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON rivington.* TO rivington@localhost IDENTIFIED BY 'rivington'"

Initialize the table:

  $ mysql --user=rivington -p < data/rivington.sql

Backing up the database:

  $ mysqldump --user=rivington -p > rivington.sql


